">. &nbsp;And the results weren’t what we expected.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZHuYgoc8x_text","label":"ggZHuYgoc8x_text","default":"After Testing All 21 Collagen Masks,&nbsp;<br>Here's What We Found:"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvDN5djePx_text","label":"ggvDN5djePx_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(242, 255, 5, 0.77);color:#000000;\"><strong>Out of the 21 that were tested, only 5 stood out.</strong></span></p><p><br>And the Number 1 among the 5 wasn't the most expensive or the most hyped, scoring a 4.8 out of 5 while the second-place mask only hit 4.1. It delivered results that lasted 7 days from a single use, while bigger brands faded in 1-2 days.</p><p><br>If you're confused about ingredients, worried about reactions, or tired of products that promise results without any proof, this is for you.</p>"}],
